00:01:25.050 --> 00:01:28.170
[Whispers of Fate]

00:01:28.410 --> 00:01:29.950
[Episode 38]

00:01:37.120 --> 00:01:39.180
Why is Master only just getting back?

00:01:39.400 --> 00:01:41.800
Why has he been acting
so secretive lately?

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:44.710
Chunji?

00:01:45.360 --> 00:01:46.080
Master.

00:01:46.110 --> 00:01:47.710
You're still up at this hour?

00:01:48.350 --> 00:01:49.950
Where are your royal guards?

00:01:51.080 --> 00:01:53.070
It's actually quite uncomfortable

00:01:53.070 --> 00:01:54.930
being followed by them every day.

00:01:56.610 --> 00:01:57.280
Besides,

00:01:57.800 --> 00:01:59.310
I grew up here.

00:01:59.670 --> 00:02:00.800
This is my home.

00:02:01.080 --> 00:02:01.910
Who would want

00:02:01.910 --> 00:02:03.840
to be followed around even at home?

00:02:05.110 --> 00:02:06.030
I remember when you

00:02:06.030 --> 00:02:07.160
first came here—

00:02:07.360 --> 00:02:08.389
you sat right here

00:02:08.590 --> 00:02:10.199
watching me practice calligraphy.

00:02:10.199 --> 00:02:11.270
You were so mischievous,

00:02:11.270 --> 00:02:12.710
sneakily drawing on my face

00:02:12.710 --> 00:02:14.040
while I was sleeping.

00:02:15.430 --> 00:02:16.630
In the blink of an eye,

00:02:16.710 --> 00:02:17.910
you've grown so much.

00:02:37.360 --> 00:02:38.090
Yes, indeed.

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:40.860
Later, you taught me swordsmanship.

00:02:41.320 --> 00:02:42.980
Because this place is remote,

00:02:43.960 --> 00:02:46.270
I could continue practicing here at night

00:02:46.270 --> 00:02:49.530
whatever swordsmanship I couldn't master
during the day.

00:02:52.760 --> 00:02:54.420
It seems like it's been so long

00:02:55.480 --> 00:02:56.270
since I've had a heart-to-heart talk

00:02:56.270 --> 00:02:57.800
with you like this, Master.

00:02:58.270 --> 00:02:58.960
Chunji,

00:02:59.870 --> 00:03:01.110
do you resent me?

00:03:03.110 --> 00:03:04.040
I wouldn't dare.

00:03:04.520 --> 00:03:05.380
Wouldn't dare?

00:03:05.990 --> 00:03:07.190
Then you do resent me.

00:03:08.100 --> 00:03:09.170
It's my fault

00:03:09.270 --> 00:03:11.800
for raising you to be
too demanding of yourself.

00:03:11.800 --> 00:03:13.330
You've always worked hard,

00:03:13.430 --> 00:03:14.890
always seeking approval.

00:03:15.990 --> 00:03:17.040
I...

00:03:18.440 --> 00:03:20.440
have indeed failed you in some ways.

00:03:22.990 --> 00:03:23.430
No.

00:03:27.079 --> 00:03:29.210
I am the one who has failed you, Master.

00:03:31.040 --> 00:03:31.710
Master...

00:03:34.480 --> 00:03:35.590
If one day

00:03:36.920 --> 00:03:37.870
you discover...

00:03:40.960 --> 00:03:42.560
Just say what you want to say.

00:03:43.390 --> 00:03:44.870
If you discover I've done

00:03:45.550 --> 00:03:47.670
many wrong things behind your back

00:03:47.670 --> 00:03:49.670
and told many lies...

00:03:50.640 --> 00:03:52.040
Actually, I didn't cook

00:03:52.480 --> 00:03:54.340
the medicinal porridge that day.

00:03:57.800 --> 00:03:59.270
You think I didn't notice?

00:04:00.340 --> 00:04:02.550
You couldn't even roast a sweet potato
when you were little.

00:04:02.550 --> 00:04:03.550
That porridge was

00:04:03.550 --> 00:04:05.830
fresh, fragrant, sweet,
and rich in ingredients.

00:04:05.830 --> 00:04:06.960
It was clearly made

00:04:07.240 --> 00:04:08.270
by a palace cook.

00:04:09.040 --> 00:04:10.550
Nothing escapes your notice, Master.

00:04:10.550 --> 00:04:11.270
Of course.

00:04:15.550 --> 00:04:16.200
It's late.

00:04:16.680 --> 00:04:18.410
I'll walk you back to your room.

00:04:23.200 --> 00:04:24.030
Zhong Chunji,

00:04:25.000 --> 00:04:26.800
why have you become so cowardly?

00:04:27.590 --> 00:04:28.230
Tomorrow.

00:04:29.030 --> 00:04:31.080
I'll definitely confess everything
to Master tomorrow.

00:04:31.080 --> 00:04:31.640
Come on.

00:04:31.830 --> 00:04:33.159
Time to go back to sleep.

00:04:34.150 --> 00:04:34.909
Coming.

00:04:36.790 --> 00:04:37.390
Master.

00:04:38.590 --> 00:04:40.720
It feels like I'm back in my childhood.

00:04:55.000 --> 00:04:56.350
Orders from Sword Master Tang:

00:04:56.350 --> 00:04:57.810
While Mr. Chi is detained,

00:04:57.960 --> 00:04:59.820
no one is allowed to approach him.

00:05:01.470 --> 00:05:02.790
I've brought some food and wine

00:05:02.790 --> 00:05:04.030
and just want to see him briefly.

00:05:04.030 --> 00:05:04.830
Food is allowed,

00:05:04.830 --> 00:05:05.760
but after our inspection,

00:05:05.760 --> 00:05:07.080
we'll deliver it for you, miss.

00:05:07.080 --> 00:05:08.350
We have our duties to fulfill.

00:05:08.350 --> 00:05:09.480
Please understand.

00:05:15.880 --> 00:05:16.760
Of course, I understand.

00:05:16.760 --> 00:05:18.020
I'm the one intruding.

00:05:18.200 --> 00:05:18.930
Well then...

00:05:20.350 --> 00:05:21.880
I'll trouble you with this.

00:05:42.270 --> 00:05:43.930
With this final vial of serum,

00:05:44.350 --> 00:05:45.390
Chi Yun should be able to hold on

00:05:45.390 --> 00:05:46.920
until the antidote is made.

00:05:48.000 --> 00:05:48.590
Mr. Tang!

00:05:49.440 --> 00:05:50.500
Mr. Tang, bad news.

00:05:50.640 --> 00:05:52.030
Chi's poison has flared up.

00:05:52.030 --> 00:05:54.630
He injured the guards
and broke out of the cell.

00:05:57.880 --> 00:05:59.409
Chi Yun was fine yesterday.

00:05:59.620 --> 00:06:01.820
How could his poison suddenly flare up?

00:06:01.910 --> 00:06:02.770
The guards said

00:06:02.880 --> 00:06:04.410
Xifang Tao came yesterday.

00:06:04.710 --> 00:06:06.170
But they didn't let her in.

00:06:19.880 --> 00:06:21.540
Enemy attack on the fortress.

00:06:22.160 --> 00:06:23.330
Disaster imminent.

00:06:24.680 --> 00:06:26.120
Extremely urgent.

00:06:26.880 --> 00:06:28.150
Return immediately.

00:06:32.640 --> 00:06:33.470
He escaped?

00:06:36.520 --> 00:06:38.120
How could you let him escape?

00:06:38.230 --> 00:06:39.690
If his poison has erupted,

00:06:39.720 --> 00:06:40.680
the villagers at the foot of the mountain

00:06:40.680 --> 00:06:41.680
will be in danger.

00:06:42.960 --> 00:06:44.760
How could you all be so careless?

00:06:49.820 --> 00:06:51.440
Xifang Tao!

00:06:59.640 --> 00:07:00.390
Miss Xifang.

00:07:38.620 --> 00:07:41.590
[Central Plains Sword Alliance]

00:07:42.830 --> 00:07:45.890
-Hello, Sword Master Tang.
-Hello, Sword Master Tang.

00:07:46.880 --> 00:07:47.409
Let's go.

00:07:48.200 --> 00:07:49.030
Mr. Tang!

00:07:49.880 --> 00:07:51.880
I already know about the situation.

00:07:51.880 --> 00:07:53.960
There's something suspicious
about Chi Yun's sudden madness.

00:07:53.960 --> 00:07:56.760
It may be dangerous for you
to search for him alone.

00:07:57.830 --> 00:07:59.560
Shui Duopo came to me last night

00:07:59.680 --> 00:08:01.200
and said the prescription this time

00:08:01.200 --> 00:08:02.660
is absolutely foolproof.

00:08:03.080 --> 00:08:04.460
Once this matter is settled,

00:08:04.460 --> 00:08:05.790
my worries

00:08:05.790 --> 00:08:06.920
will mostly be gone.

00:08:07.270 --> 00:08:08.530
As for finding Mr. Chi,

00:08:08.590 --> 00:08:10.350
let the Sword Alliance help you.

00:08:10.350 --> 00:08:11.080
Master Shao.

00:08:11.520 --> 00:08:12.270
I'll handle

00:08:13.230 --> 00:08:14.630
Chi Yun's matter myself.

00:08:16.440 --> 00:08:17.080
Wait!

00:08:18.830 --> 00:08:19.390
You...

00:08:21.080 --> 00:08:23.080
Don't push yourself too hard.

00:08:23.880 --> 00:08:25.030
Don't try to shoulder

00:08:25.030 --> 00:08:26.230
everything alone.

00:08:26.490 --> 00:08:27.960
And don't treat the help of others

00:08:27.960 --> 00:08:29.120
as a burden!

00:08:30.780 --> 00:08:31.540
Mr. Tang,

00:08:31.910 --> 00:08:33.080
you're still young.

00:08:33.690 --> 00:08:34.230
You have a long road

00:08:34.230 --> 00:08:35.590
ahead of you.

00:08:36.539 --> 00:08:37.780
Everyone, sooner or later,

00:08:37.780 --> 00:08:39.539
grows weary and lonely.

00:08:41.400 --> 00:08:43.280
The jianghu is in turmoil.

00:08:44.080 --> 00:08:44.990
Having someone by your side

00:08:44.990 --> 00:08:47.050
is always better than walking alone!

00:08:51.200 --> 00:08:51.960
Master Shao,

00:08:52.670 --> 00:08:55.330
Xifang Tao still has allies
in the Sword Alliance.

00:08:55.330 --> 00:08:55.830
You need to stay

00:08:55.830 --> 00:08:57.350
to prevent internal conflict.

00:08:57.350 --> 00:08:58.110
But you...

00:09:11.680 --> 00:09:12.850
Mr. Tang.

00:09:13.230 --> 00:09:14.680
I once thought you could be

00:09:14.680 --> 00:09:16.000
the one to shake up the jianghu

00:09:16.000 --> 00:09:17.790
and reshape its order.

00:09:18.580 --> 00:09:20.630
But circumstances shift without warning,

00:09:20.630 --> 00:09:23.400
and and we who are caught in the game
can only submit to fate.

00:09:23.400 --> 00:09:24.790
I hope that one day

00:09:25.320 --> 00:09:27.080
you'll stop forcing yourself

00:09:27.790 --> 00:09:29.910
and learn to take care of yourself.

00:09:43.200 --> 00:09:43.990
Stone,

00:09:44.440 --> 00:09:46.350
Master Tang's friend is in trouble.

00:09:46.350 --> 00:09:47.320
Instead of going to comfort him,

00:09:47.320 --> 00:09:48.650
what are you doing here?

00:09:49.830 --> 00:09:50.710
Planting a tree.

00:09:50.710 --> 00:09:51.640
Planting a tree?

00:09:51.680 --> 00:09:52.810
Why plant a tree now?

00:09:53.110 --> 00:09:54.110
Just...

00:09:55.080 --> 00:09:55.960
suddenly...

00:09:56.630 --> 00:09:57.280
need to...

00:09:58.110 --> 00:09:58.840
plant a tree.

00:10:00.280 --> 00:10:01.340
Let's go. Let's go.

00:10:01.960 --> 00:10:04.000
Why is Stone acting so strangely today?

00:10:04.000 --> 00:10:05.670
Usually he clings to Mr. Tang,

00:10:06.080 --> 00:10:07.560
but now that something this serious
has happened,

00:10:07.560 --> 00:10:08.590
how can he still be so calm

00:10:08.590 --> 00:10:09.790
planting a tree here?

00:10:14.400 --> 00:10:15.160
Master!

00:10:21.200 --> 00:10:22.750
Master seems distracted

00:10:22.870 --> 00:10:24.330
and is carrying medicine.

00:10:24.420 --> 00:10:26.420
Is he going to deliver it to someone?

00:10:29.400 --> 00:10:32.000
Chi Yun's incident
definitely wasn't an accident.

00:10:32.000 --> 00:10:34.230
I must deliver this prescription quickly,

00:10:34.230 --> 00:10:36.090
before anything else goes wrong.

00:10:45.710 --> 00:10:47.680
Master Shao, you're in such a hurry.

00:10:47.680 --> 00:10:49.200
Where are you heading?

00:10:56.200 --> 00:10:56.920
Who are you?

00:11:28.350 --> 00:11:29.150
Master...

00:11:37.830 --> 00:11:38.440
Master!

00:11:39.630 --> 00:11:40.440
Who are you?

00:11:40.540 --> 00:11:41.870
Why did you hurt my master?

00:11:41.870 --> 00:11:42.510
Chunji.

00:11:42.800 --> 00:11:44.160
Leave me behind and run.

00:11:44.560 --> 00:11:46.160
How could I leave you behind?

00:11:52.160 --> 00:11:53.110
Only a tool

00:11:53.520 --> 00:11:55.130
can be a true tool.

00:11:56.510 --> 00:11:57.440
Nice to meet you.

00:11:57.710 --> 00:11:58.680
You can call me

00:11:59.400 --> 00:12:00.350
Ghostly Peony.

00:12:00.960 --> 00:12:03.110
Ghostly Peony, you're still alive?

00:12:03.560 --> 00:12:04.160
Chunji,

00:12:04.470 --> 00:12:05.930
fire the signal flare now!

00:12:09.570 --> 00:12:11.770
Have you thought it through, Princess?

00:12:12.630 --> 00:12:13.440
Xifang Tao,

00:12:14.040 --> 00:12:14.830
what exactly are you

00:12:14.830 --> 00:12:16.560
and Ghostly Peony trying to do?

00:12:21.630 --> 00:12:22.320
Godfather, looks like

00:12:22.320 --> 00:12:23.720
you've fully recovered.

00:12:24.280 --> 00:12:25.710
Liu Yan betrayed us.

00:12:26.470 --> 00:12:28.160
The poisoned people have been

00:12:28.160 --> 00:12:30.040
transferred to Sword King City
by Tang Lici.

00:12:30.040 --> 00:12:31.510
This amount of Black Tuli

00:12:31.510 --> 00:12:32.650
is far from enough.

00:12:33.510 --> 00:12:34.560
Godfather, you haven't given up

00:12:34.560 --> 00:12:35.960
on our master's mission.

00:12:36.040 --> 00:12:36.800
I heard

00:12:37.350 --> 00:12:38.990
the bronze tree has been destroyed,

00:12:38.990 --> 00:12:40.650
and our master's plan failed.

00:12:41.510 --> 00:12:43.510
Don't you want freedom, Godfather?

00:12:44.440 --> 00:12:45.040
Freedom?

00:12:46.470 --> 00:12:47.200
The freedom to decide

00:12:47.200 --> 00:12:48.400
your own destiny.

00:12:50.230 --> 00:12:51.830
Why do I need freedom?

00:12:52.400 --> 00:12:53.440
A bottle exists

00:12:53.440 --> 00:12:55.080
to hold water.

00:12:56.190 --> 00:12:57.360
A free bottle

00:12:57.710 --> 00:12:59.370
is nothing but useless trash.

00:13:00.110 --> 00:13:01.110
Strings are meant

00:13:01.920 --> 00:13:04.380
to be tied to the tuning pegs
of instruments.

00:13:05.110 --> 00:13:06.470
Free strings

00:13:07.710 --> 00:13:09.170
are just useless threads.

00:13:09.830 --> 00:13:11.230
But people aren't tools.

00:13:12.200 --> 00:13:14.200
Perhaps a bottle wants to hold wine.

00:13:14.590 --> 00:13:15.520
Perhaps strings

00:13:16.280 --> 00:13:17.680
want to be fishing lines.

00:13:18.160 --> 00:13:19.350
That's merely changing

00:13:19.350 --> 00:13:21.150
from one kind of tool to another.

00:13:21.830 --> 00:13:23.490
People who find their purpose

00:13:23.870 --> 00:13:25.160
are useful tools.

00:13:26.040 --> 00:13:27.970
Those who can't find their purpose

00:13:28.440 --> 00:13:29.370
are no different

00:13:29.710 --> 00:13:30.710
from trash.

00:13:31.400 --> 00:13:33.600
Only after dying once did I understand.

00:13:33.800 --> 00:13:35.400
As long as our master lives,

00:13:35.420 --> 00:13:36.940
a puppet remains a puppet.

00:13:37.160 --> 00:13:39.160
Even with thoughts and feelings...

00:13:40.560 --> 00:13:41.760
how is that different

00:13:42.590 --> 00:13:43.800
from being a tool?

00:13:44.710 --> 00:13:47.110
Rather than discussing illusory freedom,

00:13:47.960 --> 00:13:49.510
Godfather, why don't you just tell me

00:13:49.510 --> 00:13:50.710
what you want me to do?

00:13:50.990 --> 00:13:52.680
I need more Black Tuli.

00:13:53.230 --> 00:13:54.440
Tang Lici...

00:13:55.360 --> 00:13:57.040
keeps ruining my plans.

00:13:59.040 --> 00:14:01.200
Godfather, your trap in West Wind Garden

00:14:01.200 --> 00:14:02.800
wasn't completely useless.

00:14:03.590 --> 00:14:04.590
Chi Yun's poisoning

00:14:04.590 --> 00:14:05.830
has already consumed most of

00:14:05.830 --> 00:14:06.960
Tang Lici's energy.

00:14:08.080 --> 00:14:08.990
So, he'll definitely

00:14:08.990 --> 00:14:09.990
have someone else

00:14:09.990 --> 00:14:10.920
contact Liu Yan.

00:14:11.870 --> 00:14:13.200
Whoever that person is,

00:14:14.080 --> 00:14:15.410
following them gives us

00:14:15.830 --> 00:14:17.960
a much better chance of finding Liu Yan

00:14:17.960 --> 00:14:19.420
than following Tang Lici.

00:14:30.040 --> 00:14:30.700
Godfather.

00:14:31.630 --> 00:14:32.440
I've already searched

00:14:32.440 --> 00:14:33.990
for clues in the direction

00:14:34.200 --> 00:14:35.600
Master Shao was heading.

00:14:36.160 --> 00:14:38.230
There's a small mountain village ahead.

00:14:38.230 --> 00:14:39.630
Liu Yan is indeed there.

00:14:40.920 --> 00:14:42.280
Still one step too late.

00:14:42.800 --> 00:14:43.320
No.

00:14:43.800 --> 00:14:44.830
I must let Mr. Tang know

00:14:44.830 --> 00:14:45.800
that Ghostly Peony is

00:14:45.800 --> 00:14:47.320
behind Xifang Tao.

00:14:48.040 --> 00:14:49.200
Between Chunji and me,

00:14:49.200 --> 00:14:51.160
one of us must make it out alive.

00:14:51.670 --> 00:14:52.400
Princess.

00:14:53.350 --> 00:14:54.040
Have you decided

00:14:54.040 --> 00:14:55.770
which side you want to stand on?

00:14:55.980 --> 00:14:57.910
Princess, you're a clever person.

00:14:58.110 --> 00:14:59.920
Coming here from the Sword Alliance

00:14:59.920 --> 00:15:01.380
will take at least an hour.

00:15:02.120 --> 00:15:03.040
An hour

00:15:03.510 --> 00:15:04.840
is more than enough time

00:15:05.160 --> 00:15:06.590
for us to kill Master Shao

00:15:07.830 --> 00:15:09.200
and spare your life.

00:15:09.920 --> 00:15:10.980
When that happens,

00:15:11.110 --> 00:15:12.940
we'll simply tell everyone

00:15:13.400 --> 00:15:14.470
that Master Shao

00:15:15.160 --> 00:15:17.040
discovered you were an impostor,

00:15:17.990 --> 00:15:20.160
that you killed your master

00:15:20.440 --> 00:15:21.990
to preserve your wealth and status,

00:15:21.990 --> 00:15:23.200
and that I,

00:15:23.400 --> 00:15:25.000
Xifang Tao, arrived too late

00:15:25.000 --> 00:15:26.710
to save him.

00:15:27.560 --> 00:15:29.420
You think people will believe you

00:15:30.470 --> 00:15:31.800
just because you say so?

00:15:32.200 --> 00:15:33.410
What I just said

00:15:33.680 --> 00:15:34.680
is indeed false.

00:15:35.110 --> 00:15:37.510
But the fake tattoo on your body

00:15:37.880 --> 00:15:39.670
is enough to turn my lies

00:15:40.300 --> 00:15:41.300
into truth.

00:15:42.200 --> 00:15:42.920
After all, wouldn't the words

00:15:42.920 --> 00:15:44.520
of an innocent person like me

00:15:45.350 --> 00:15:47.040
be more credible than those of

00:15:47.350 --> 00:15:49.750
someone who's definitely a fake princess?

00:15:50.750 --> 00:15:51.320
Chunji,

00:15:52.280 --> 00:15:53.740
is what she's saying true?

00:15:57.380 --> 00:15:57.990
Princess,

00:15:58.870 --> 00:16:00.870
are you willing to take that gamble?

00:16:04.750 --> 00:16:05.550
Tai'e Sword's

00:16:05.870 --> 00:16:06.470
Offering!

00:16:07.550 --> 00:16:09.150
Heaven-Changing Scripture—

00:16:09.150 --> 00:16:10.680
Reverse Yin and Yang.

00:16:16.680 --> 00:16:17.350
Chunji,

00:16:17.750 --> 00:16:18.830
I once said

00:16:19.320 --> 00:16:20.920
that we should be good people

00:16:20.920 --> 00:16:22.380
even if it comes at a price.

00:16:22.400 --> 00:16:23.000
Remember,

00:16:23.340 --> 00:16:24.860
I never blamed you.

00:16:25.830 --> 00:16:26.830
Chunji, run!

00:16:27.130 --> 00:16:28.290
You must survive

00:16:28.620 --> 00:16:29.400
and tell everyone

00:16:29.400 --> 00:16:30.870
that Ghostly Peony is still alive!

