-A poisoned person!
-A poisoned person!

00:21:33.230 --> 00:21:33.750
Run!

00:21:33.880 --> 00:21:34.440
Hurry! Run!

00:21:34.440 --> 00:21:35.440
Let's go get help!

00:21:45.790 --> 00:21:46.680
Darn it.

00:21:47.470 --> 00:21:48.800
Is he somewhere nearby?

00:21:49.360 --> 00:21:50.550
Where?

00:21:50.840 --> 00:21:51.600
Where did he go?

00:21:51.600 --> 00:21:52.270
Exactly.

00:21:53.350 --> 00:21:53.750
There.

00:21:54.600 --> 00:21:55.330
Look at that.

00:21:55.710 --> 00:21:56.570
That one ahead!

00:21:57.230 --> 00:21:57.840
Hey, man!

00:21:58.310 --> 00:22:00.360
You're looking for Huoyun Fortress, right?

00:22:00.360 --> 00:22:01.960
We're from Huoyun Fortress.

00:22:04.310 --> 00:22:05.230
Are you blind?

00:22:05.790 --> 00:22:06.270
Boss?

00:22:06.270 --> 00:22:06.790
Chi?

00:22:08.310 --> 00:22:09.070
How could you not recognize me?

00:22:09.070 --> 00:22:10.330
Boss, it really is you!

00:22:11.470 --> 00:22:12.880
What happened to your face?

00:22:12.880 --> 00:22:13.680
It's nothing.

00:22:13.840 --> 00:22:14.880
I got a bit poisoned.

00:22:14.880 --> 00:22:15.480
Poisoned?

00:22:16.160 --> 00:22:16.710
Where's the bastard

00:22:16.710 --> 00:22:17.710
who poisoned you?

00:22:17.840 --> 00:22:18.230
Guys,

00:22:18.470 --> 00:22:19.310
let's avenge our boss!

00:22:19.310 --> 00:22:20.880
-Yes, avenge our boss!
-Yes, avenge our boss!

00:22:20.880 --> 00:22:21.940
Alright, alright.

00:22:22.400 --> 00:22:23.800
That one is already dead.

00:22:24.820 --> 00:22:25.950
Why are you all here?

00:22:26.600 --> 00:22:27.260
The letter.

00:22:27.550 --> 00:22:28.750
We came to rescue you.

00:22:28.790 --> 00:22:29.600
Look.

00:22:29.600 --> 00:22:31.330
We received a distress letter.

00:22:31.960 --> 00:22:33.230
I never wrote this.

00:22:34.780 --> 00:22:35.780
Who sent it to you?

00:22:36.070 --> 00:22:36.920
It's forged?

00:22:36.920 --> 00:22:37.790
Forged?

00:22:38.070 --> 00:22:40.510
The rogue went through all this trouble
to forge a letter.

00:22:40.510 --> 00:22:41.360
What for?

00:22:42.310 --> 00:22:42.910
Who cares?

00:22:43.160 --> 00:22:44.640
As long as we got to see our boss here,

00:22:44.640 --> 00:22:45.970
the trip wasn't wasted.

00:22:46.510 --> 00:22:47.360
-That's right.
-Yeah!

00:22:47.360 --> 00:22:48.070
Today, let's have

00:22:48.070 --> 00:22:48.990
a good drink together,

00:22:48.990 --> 00:22:49.850
get some sleep,

00:22:49.920 --> 00:22:50.710
and everything will be fine
when we wake up.

00:22:50.710 --> 00:22:52.030
-Yes, absolutely.
-Yeah.

00:22:52.030 --> 00:22:52.470
Let's go.

00:22:52.470 --> 00:22:53.230
-Come on, let's drink.
-Let's go.

00:22:53.230 --> 00:22:54.760
-Let's go drink.
-Let's go.

00:22:55.200 --> 00:22:55.680
Boss.

00:22:56.310 --> 00:22:57.470
When you left the fortress back then,

00:22:57.470 --> 00:22:58.070
we all thought

00:22:58.070 --> 00:22:59.130
you'd be back soon.

00:22:59.550 --> 00:23:00.750
We've all missed you.

00:23:01.360 --> 00:23:01.920
I also...

00:23:04.960 --> 00:23:05.690
Why don't...

00:23:07.030 --> 00:23:07.840
you all come back with me

00:23:07.840 --> 00:23:08.960
to the Central Plains Sword Alliance?

00:23:08.960 --> 00:23:10.360
That would be wonderful.

00:23:10.360 --> 00:23:10.760
But...

00:23:11.070 --> 00:23:13.160
We're all bandits who rule the mountain.

00:23:13.160 --> 00:23:14.310
Will the alliance accept us?

00:23:14.310 --> 00:23:15.160
We are...

00:23:16.160 --> 00:23:17.200
chivalrous bandits

00:23:17.200 --> 00:23:19.000
who rob the rich to help the poor.

00:23:19.070 --> 00:23:20.200
Bandits? What's that supposed to mean?

00:23:20.200 --> 00:23:22.070
I'm well-connected
in the Central Plains Sword Alliance.

00:23:22.070 --> 00:23:22.750
My reputation is formidable.

00:23:22.750 --> 00:23:23.820
They'll definitely accept you.

00:23:23.820 --> 00:23:24.840
Boss is so impressive.

00:23:24.840 --> 00:23:25.370
Let's go.

00:23:25.950 --> 00:23:26.400
Boss.

00:23:27.120 --> 00:23:29.160
That runaway fiancée of yours...

00:23:29.160 --> 00:23:30.090
did you find her?

00:23:43.400 --> 00:23:44.270
Chi Yun!

00:23:46.550 --> 00:23:47.070
Boss?

00:23:47.200 --> 00:23:49.730
If you can't remember,
don't force yourself.

00:23:50.660 --> 00:23:51.790
What exactly did I forget?

00:23:51.790 --> 00:23:53.120
Boss, it's me, Datou!

00:23:53.120 --> 00:23:54.310
Boss, are you alright?

00:23:54.310 --> 00:23:55.910
Don't you even recognize me?

00:23:58.560 --> 00:23:59.340
Wake up!

00:24:07.550 --> 00:24:09.680
He's been poisoned
by the Blood Ghost Pill.

00:24:09.680 --> 00:24:11.540
He can't recognize any of you now.

00:24:14.790 --> 00:24:15.550
Who are you?

00:24:15.970 --> 00:24:17.370
What did you just feed me?

00:24:17.960 --> 00:24:18.990
Mr. Tang sent me

00:24:18.990 --> 00:24:19.920
to take you back.

00:24:20.130 --> 00:24:20.860
Come with me.

00:24:21.030 --> 00:24:21.840
Foxy Tang?

00:24:23.120 --> 00:24:24.320
How come I didn't know

00:24:24.670 --> 00:24:26.120
he had a woman by his side?

00:24:26.550 --> 00:24:27.550
He figured out so quickly

00:24:27.550 --> 00:24:28.810
the letter was forged?

00:24:30.080 --> 00:24:31.360
Why do you wear a mask?

00:24:32.440 --> 00:24:34.300
Why do you have so many questions?

00:24:34.920 --> 00:24:36.310
What's your surname then?

00:24:36.310 --> 00:24:37.310
My surname is Bai.

00:24:39.430 --> 00:24:40.290
-Let's go.
-Go.

00:24:45.360 --> 00:24:46.750
This road is the only way

00:24:46.750 --> 00:24:47.880
to Huoyun Fortress.

00:24:48.360 --> 00:24:49.120
Following this path,

00:24:49.120 --> 00:24:51.320
I should be able to catch up with Chi Yun.

00:24:51.880 --> 00:24:53.160
White Stone Formation?

00:24:53.160 --> 00:24:54.020
It's Bai Suche.

00:24:54.440 --> 00:24:55.640
She has found Chi Yun.

00:25:00.880 --> 00:25:01.940
It's getting dark.

00:25:01.990 --> 00:25:03.840
Even if we're in a hurry,
we should fill our stomachs first, right?

00:25:03.840 --> 00:25:04.200
Boss,

00:25:04.200 --> 00:25:04.750
look over there.

00:25:04.750 --> 00:25:04.940
Isn't that an inn?

00:25:04.940 --> 00:25:07.200
[Baiwei Inn]

00:25:07.200 --> 00:25:07.960
Guys, guys.

00:25:08.230 --> 00:25:10.030
I don't even know
if the Mind-Clearing Pill will last

00:25:10.030 --> 00:25:11.840
until he returns to the Sword Alliance.

00:25:11.840 --> 00:25:13.840
And now they've detoured for a meal.

00:25:14.840 --> 00:25:15.680
I must quickly

00:25:15.680 --> 00:25:16.360
get them back

00:25:16.360 --> 00:25:17.490
on the original path

00:25:17.790 --> 00:25:19.120
to avoid missing Mr. Tang.

00:25:19.120 --> 00:25:20.450
This wine is excellent.

00:25:20.510 --> 00:25:21.510
He's even drinking now?

00:25:21.510 --> 00:25:22.230
The wine is so good.

00:25:22.230 --> 00:25:23.270
I saved it especially for you, Boss!

00:25:23.270 --> 00:25:24.400
Good wine! Cheers!

00:25:25.230 --> 00:25:26.510
We need to get back on the road soon.

00:25:26.510 --> 00:25:27.440
You can't drink.

