00:25:41.680 --> 00:25:42.160
Sir!

00:25:43.400 --> 00:25:44.270
What can I get you?

00:25:44.270 --> 00:25:45.130
Bring me a pot of tea.

00:25:45.130 --> 00:25:45.990
You guys drink.

00:25:46.230 --> 00:25:46.890
Right away.

00:25:47.510 --> 00:25:48.360
Why do you want tea, Boss?

00:25:48.360 --> 00:25:49.160
Yeah, Boss.

00:25:49.310 --> 00:25:50.410
Did I hear that right?

00:25:50.410 --> 00:25:51.140
You want tea?

00:25:51.600 --> 00:25:52.330
Tea? Really?

00:25:52.470 --> 00:25:53.030
Enough.

00:25:53.790 --> 00:25:54.790
You don't understand.

00:25:54.790 --> 00:25:56.360
I drank adulterated wine twice in a row.

00:25:56.360 --> 00:25:57.200
After drinking, my head was spinning,

00:25:57.200 --> 00:25:58.840
and I couldn't remember anything.

00:25:58.840 --> 00:26:00.300
It's better to drink less.

00:26:02.440 --> 00:26:04.300
Waiter, hurry up with our dishes!

00:26:04.300 --> 00:26:05.430
You can't get drunk.

00:26:05.690 --> 00:26:06.680
We need to head to

00:26:06.680 --> 00:26:07.930
the Central Plains Sword Alliance soon.

00:26:07.930 --> 00:26:09.330
We'll leave in two hours.

00:26:10.880 --> 00:26:12.140
You all heard that, eh?

00:26:12.280 --> 00:26:12.940
Drink less.

00:26:13.600 --> 00:26:15.260
Come on, customers, this way.

00:26:15.270 --> 00:26:17.070
-Come on, let's drink.
-Come on.

00:26:19.070 --> 00:26:19.600
Boss.

00:26:20.360 --> 00:26:21.550
Does that girl

00:26:21.550 --> 00:26:22.810
have something on you?

00:26:22.900 --> 00:26:24.270
How much money do you owe her?

00:26:24.270 --> 00:26:25.790
We can all chip in
and help you pay it off.

00:26:25.790 --> 00:26:26.480
-That's right, Boss.
-Yeah.

00:26:26.480 --> 00:26:27.810
-Yeah.
-We can help out.

00:26:28.030 --> 00:26:30.470
Stop talking nonsense.
You don't understand.

00:26:30.470 --> 00:26:31.680
She cares about me.

00:26:31.960 --> 00:26:33.510
That's why she's so controlling.

00:26:33.510 --> 00:26:34.640
I don't know why.

00:26:35.120 --> 00:26:36.550
But when she scolds me...

00:26:36.880 --> 00:26:37.470
Please, go upstairs.

00:26:37.470 --> 00:26:38.590
I actually kind of like it.

00:26:38.590 --> 00:26:39.070
Boss?

00:26:39.070 --> 00:26:39.550
You're not falling for her

00:26:39.550 --> 00:26:41.480
just because of her looks, are you?

00:26:41.840 --> 00:26:42.750
Falling for her looks?

00:26:42.750 --> 00:26:44.360
Then we'd have to see
what she looks like first.

00:26:44.360 --> 00:26:46.020
We haven't even seen her face.

00:26:46.200 --> 00:26:47.310
She's always wearing a veil

00:26:47.310 --> 00:26:48.710
and never shows her face.

00:26:49.030 --> 00:26:50.430
That can't be right, man.

00:26:50.470 --> 00:26:51.710
-Yeah, exactly.
-Yeah.

00:26:51.710 --> 00:26:52.370
I get it now.

00:26:52.750 --> 00:26:54.270
She must be incredibly ugly,

00:26:54.270 --> 00:26:55.470
and that's why she doesn't show her face.

00:26:55.470 --> 00:26:56.070
Maybe

00:26:56.640 --> 00:26:57.920
her face is covered in pockmarks,

00:26:57.920 --> 00:26:59.270
with a crooked mouth and squinting eyes.

00:26:59.270 --> 00:26:59.880
Right?

00:26:59.880 --> 00:27:01.210
-Yes, exactly.
-Right.

00:27:01.230 --> 00:27:01.960
Am I right?

00:27:01.960 --> 00:27:03.220
-That's right.
-Yeah.

00:27:03.680 --> 00:27:05.030
A bunch of scoundrels.

00:27:06.600 --> 00:27:07.860
But come to think of it,

00:27:08.790 --> 00:27:09.550
I don't think

00:27:10.240 --> 00:27:11.470
she was being harsh with me.

00:27:11.470 --> 00:27:12.310
She actually likes me.

00:27:12.310 --> 00:27:13.240
What do you mean?

00:27:13.710 --> 00:27:14.550
I'm serious.

00:27:14.990 --> 00:27:16.320
When I see her, she feels

00:27:16.540 --> 00:27:17.410
very familiar.

00:27:17.480 --> 00:27:18.650
When she's harsh with me,

00:27:18.650 --> 00:27:19.680
it feels like

00:27:19.680 --> 00:27:20.440
my long-awaited wish

00:27:20.440 --> 00:27:21.700
has finally come true.

00:27:23.230 --> 00:27:24.090
Take care, sir.

00:27:24.600 --> 00:27:26.600
There's a feeling of satisfaction.

00:27:27.200 --> 00:27:28.070
Although I don't know

00:27:28.070 --> 00:27:28.640
why.

00:27:28.640 --> 00:27:30.710
Boss, your tolerance for alcohol
has gotten worse.

00:27:30.710 --> 00:27:32.960
You're talking nonsense
after just one bowl.

00:27:32.960 --> 00:27:34.200
Please, come in.

00:27:36.550 --> 00:27:38.120
Come on, let's drink.

00:27:38.120 --> 00:27:40.380
Pour it up. Drink to our heart's content.

00:27:41.120 --> 00:27:41.790
Miss,

00:27:42.230 --> 00:27:43.270
those guests

00:27:43.270 --> 00:27:44.880
have already gone upstairs to sleep.

00:27:44.880 --> 00:27:46.270
Maybe you should just let them sleep.

00:27:46.270 --> 00:27:47.800
You can continue your journey
early tomorrow morning.

00:27:47.800 --> 00:27:50.400
A few hours won't make
much difference, right?

00:27:58.160 --> 00:27:59.400
I've already called them.

00:27:59.400 --> 00:28:00.800
They should be down soon.

00:28:01.990 --> 00:28:02.710
I...

00:28:03.400 --> 00:28:05.660
If you have something to say, just say it.

00:28:06.840 --> 00:28:07.440
Did you...

00:28:08.480 --> 00:28:09.890
hear all that stuff

00:28:10.490 --> 00:28:11.640
I said earlier?

00:28:13.400 --> 00:28:15.440
You said that on purpose for me to hear?

00:28:15.440 --> 00:28:16.440
I swear to heaven!

00:28:17.230 --> 00:28:18.560
All that nonsense about

00:28:19.160 --> 00:28:20.440
"crooked mouth, squinty eyes,
and pockmarked face"—

00:28:20.440 --> 00:28:21.200
I didn't say any of that.

00:28:21.200 --> 00:28:21.930
They said it.

00:28:22.400 --> 00:28:24.200
They were all talking nonsense.

00:28:24.200 --> 00:28:25.750
They're used to running their mouths.

00:28:25.750 --> 00:28:27.750
Please don't take it to heart, miss.

00:28:28.680 --> 00:28:29.440
I don't mind.

00:28:30.360 --> 00:28:30.950
Miss Bai,

00:28:31.640 --> 00:28:33.160
do you wear that veil...

00:28:34.200 --> 00:28:35.800
because of your appearance?

00:28:37.960 --> 00:28:38.600
It's okay.

00:28:39.550 --> 00:28:40.750
After I was poisoned,

00:28:41.200 --> 00:28:42.930
people called me a monster too.

00:28:42.990 --> 00:28:43.880
When the poison flares up,

00:28:43.880 --> 00:28:44.960
I look very strange as well.

00:28:44.960 --> 00:28:46.440
People on the street even call me a demon.

00:28:46.440 --> 00:28:48.880
It's just the outer shell.
Don't let it bother you.

00:28:48.880 --> 00:28:49.550
Besides...

00:28:50.400 --> 00:28:51.440
I find it strange.

00:28:51.640 --> 00:28:53.400
I don't know why I became so attached

00:28:53.400 --> 00:28:54.880
to you the first time we met.

00:28:54.880 --> 00:28:56.740
To be honest, when I first saw you,

00:28:56.750 --> 00:28:57.750
my mind was filled

00:28:57.840 --> 00:28:58.400
with all kinds

00:28:58.400 --> 00:28:59.600
of strange thoughts.

00:28:59.640 --> 00:29:00.470
Like "I would rather die

00:29:00.470 --> 00:29:01.790
than let anything happen to you,"

00:29:01.790 --> 00:29:03.850
and even wanting to leave you a dowry.

00:29:04.200 --> 00:29:05.530
Isn't that ridiculous?

00:29:08.200 --> 00:29:10.400
Probably just hallucinations
from the poison.

00:29:10.400 --> 00:29:11.460
Don't you think...

00:29:22.910 --> 00:29:24.030
Why are you crying?

00:29:24.440 --> 00:29:25.900
Did I say something wrong?

00:29:31.120 --> 00:29:33.400
What if all of that isn't a hallucination?

00:29:33.400 --> 00:29:34.400
What if you became

00:29:34.550 --> 00:29:35.880
like this because of me?

00:29:37.120 --> 00:29:38.450
That can't be it, right?

00:29:38.680 --> 00:29:39.470
Foxy Tang said I was

00:29:39.470 --> 00:29:40.470
poisoned by someone.

00:29:40.470 --> 00:29:41.400
I was already poisoned

00:29:41.400 --> 00:29:42.330
before I met you.

00:29:42.920 --> 00:29:44.180
Could it be that you...

00:29:44.270 --> 00:29:45.160
knew me before?

00:29:46.160 --> 00:29:47.360
Foxy Tang won't tell me

00:29:47.360 --> 00:29:48.270
how I ended up poisoned.

00:29:48.270 --> 00:29:49.310
If you know,

00:29:49.310 --> 00:29:50.310
could you tell me?

00:29:51.550 --> 00:29:52.440
Can't let Chi Yun

00:29:52.440 --> 00:29:54.300
remember West Wind Garden again.

00:29:56.120 --> 00:29:57.070
When we get back to the Sword Alliance,

00:29:57.070 --> 00:29:58.130
I'll tell you then.

00:29:58.230 --> 00:29:59.690
I'll go urge them to hurry.

00:30:08.550 --> 00:30:10.950
Why such a rush to
get to the Sword Alliance?

00:30:11.200 --> 00:30:12.630
In the middle of the night,
we have to push on

00:30:12.630 --> 00:30:13.360
instead of sleeping.

00:30:13.360 --> 00:30:15.420
Just get on the road when you're told.

00:30:15.520 --> 00:30:15.920
Right,

00:30:15.960 --> 00:30:16.510
Miss Bai?

00:30:17.200 --> 00:30:18.990
Boss, why do you trust her so much?

00:30:18.990 --> 00:30:19.960
I feel like

00:30:20.120 --> 00:30:21.700
Miss Bai is deliberately taking us
on a detour.

00:30:21.700 --> 00:30:22.680
The fastest route

00:30:22.680 --> 00:30:24.440
to the Sword Alliance
goes past West Wind Garden,

00:30:24.440 --> 00:30:27.050
but she's leading us around
through the Western Ridge.

00:30:27.050 --> 00:30:28.400
West Wind Garden?

00:30:29.750 --> 00:30:30.360
Oh no!

00:30:31.270 --> 00:30:31.840
Boss?

00:30:31.840 --> 00:30:32.470
What are you trying to do

00:30:32.470 --> 00:30:33.640
to our boss, you woman?

00:30:33.640 --> 00:30:34.300
Move aside!

00:30:34.440 --> 00:30:35.440
If we don't knock him out now...

00:30:35.440 --> 00:30:35.880
Are you alright, Boss?

00:30:35.880 --> 00:30:36.920
No one will be able to stop him
once he loses control!

00:30:36.920 --> 00:30:37.790
I suspected

00:30:37.790 --> 00:30:39.160
something was wrong with you all along.

00:30:39.160 --> 00:30:39.960
Boss likes you,

00:30:39.960 --> 00:30:40.880
so I kept quiet.

00:30:41.160 --> 00:30:42.440
You've been leaving marks along the road,

00:30:42.440 --> 00:30:44.470
exposing our location the whole way.

00:30:44.470 --> 00:30:45.120
However,

00:30:45.310 --> 00:30:46.070
don't expect

00:30:46.070 --> 00:30:47.510
your accomplices to find us.

00:30:47.510 --> 00:30:49.080
I've changed all the marks you made

00:30:49.080 --> 00:30:50.640
to point in the opposite direction.

00:30:50.640 --> 00:30:52.170
You changed all my markers?

00:30:52.640 --> 00:30:53.500
Move aside now.

00:30:53.570 --> 00:30:55.070
He's about to lose control!

00:30:55.070 --> 00:30:56.360
Who are you trying to fool?

00:30:56.360 --> 00:30:57.120
We're not as

00:30:57.120 --> 00:30:58.120
gullible as Boss.

00:31:07.960 --> 00:31:09.360
This direction is wrong.

00:31:10.160 --> 00:31:12.090
Did someone tamper with the marks?

00:31:12.840 --> 00:31:14.450
Chi Yun has been missing for so long.

00:31:14.450 --> 00:31:16.510
I can't keep going in circles anymore.

00:31:16.510 --> 00:31:17.550
Soul-Seeking.

00:31:23.030 --> 00:31:23.760
Master Shao?

00:31:24.990 --> 00:31:26.430
Why is Master Shao here?

00:31:30.030 --> 00:31:30.680
Chi Yun.

00:31:42.710 --> 00:31:43.170
Boss...

00:31:43.510 --> 00:31:44.400
why?

00:31:45.920 --> 00:31:46.750
Chi Yun!

00:31:47.500 --> 00:31:48.710
Chi Yun, wake up!

00:31:48.960 --> 00:31:49.470
Chi Yun!

00:32:53.310 --> 00:32:54.240
Rebirth Scroll—

00:32:54.310 --> 00:32:54.840
Truth.

00:32:57.700 --> 00:32:58.230
Release.

00:33:43.250 --> 00:33:44.250
Chi Yun.

00:33:45.750 --> 00:33:46.550
Wake up.

00:34:07.070 --> 00:34:08.540
Boss, why...

00:34:26.880 --> 00:34:28.239
Kill me...

00:34:42.400 --> 00:34:44.280
Using your blood to suppress the poison

00:34:44.280 --> 00:34:45.239
can indeed slow

00:34:45.239 --> 00:34:46.150
its onset.

00:34:47.150 --> 00:34:48.810
But if he loses control again,

00:34:48.989 --> 00:34:50.989
it will trigger a violent backlash.

00:34:52.360 --> 00:34:53.920
At best, he'll die like the others,

00:34:53.920 --> 00:34:55.050
his body exploding.

00:34:55.679 --> 00:34:57.810
At worst, he'll become like Yu Qifeng—

00:34:58.110 --> 00:35:00.710
who knows what kind of monster
he'll turn into.

00:35:01.320 --> 00:35:02.720
If that day ever comes...

00:35:02.990 --> 00:35:04.450
I advise you to be merciful

00:35:04.590 --> 00:35:06.320
and end his suffering quickly.

00:35:59.670 --> 00:36:01.470
You just took
that old fool Yu's strike head-on,

00:36:01.470 --> 00:36:02.670
and now you want to drink?

00:36:02.670 --> 00:36:03.880
Your stomachache...

00:36:04.150 --> 00:36:05.550
I'm telling you, it's been a year,

00:36:05.550 --> 00:36:07.350
and it hasn't gotten any better.

00:36:09.670 --> 00:36:10.670
Anyway,

00:36:11.030 --> 00:36:12.470
you can't be that Yique Yinyang

00:36:12.470 --> 00:36:14.550
who brought disaster to the country.

00:36:15.240 --> 00:36:16.150
Besides,

00:36:16.590 --> 00:36:18.860
those golden eyes
and that forehead mark of yours

00:36:18.860 --> 00:36:18.960
♪ I cross the Yan River in the wasteland ♪

00:36:18.960 --> 00:36:20.420
are actually kind of cool.

00:36:24.560 --> 00:36:29.380
♪ Singing a long, unfinished song ♪

00:36:30.630 --> 00:36:31.860
♪ The full moon and a few shining stars ♪

00:36:31.860 --> 00:36:33.700
Anyone there?

00:36:35.780 --> 00:36:40.340
♪ Look down on my dream ♪

00:36:43.910 --> 00:36:44.910
Foxy Tang...

00:36:47.050 --> 00:36:47.760
♪ The breeze blows through the pleats ♪

00:36:47.760 --> 00:36:48.760
You're here.

00:36:51.810 --> 00:36:53.870
I've been waiting for you for so long.

00:36:57.360 --> 00:36:58.490
I waited from day...

00:36:58.950 --> 00:37:00.700
♪ Water polishes the old ruts ♪

00:37:00.700 --> 00:37:01.700
until night.

00:37:04.990 --> 00:37:07.190
And I waited from night until day again.

00:37:09.490 --> 00:37:10.660
But you never came.

00:37:12.060 --> 00:37:12.980
I'm sorry.

00:37:15.580 --> 00:37:16.540
I came too late.

00:37:22.190 --> 00:37:23.320
In this lifetime...

00:37:24.550 --> 00:37:26.760
I actually got to hear you apologize.

00:37:30.190 --> 00:37:30.880
But...

00:37:31.110 --> 00:37:31.880
But...

00:37:34.630 --> 00:37:35.990
I won't forgive you.

00:37:37.010 --> 00:37:38.540
Save it for our next life...

00:37:40.390 --> 00:37:41.790
when you can say it again.

00:37:53.950 --> 00:37:54.570
♪ The breeze blows through the pleats ♪

00:37:54.570 --> 00:37:55.410
I'm sorry.

00:38:05.670 --> 00:38:11.210
♪ Water polishes the old ruts ♪

00:38:14.510 --> 00:38:15.360
Chi Yun...

00:38:17.440 --> 00:38:17.700
Chi Yun...

00:38:17.700 --> 00:38:22.110
♪ Destiny entwining my fleeting life,
I can't fight ♪

00:38:22.110 --> 00:38:23.190
Say something.

00:38:24.060 --> 00:38:25.910
Say something to me, please.

00:38:26.840 --> 00:38:27.670
Chi Yun!

00:38:29.420 --> 00:38:31.730
♪ Trapped in the loop of loneliness ♪

00:38:31.730 --> 00:38:33.040
Say something.

00:38:33.780 --> 00:38:35.360
What were you about to tell me?

00:38:35.360 --> 00:38:36.490
Say it!

00:38:37.790 --> 00:38:39.420
Don't you want to marry me?

00:38:39.660 --> 00:38:40.820
I'll marry you.

00:38:40.840 --> 00:38:42.200
Please say something!

00:38:42.410 --> 00:38:43.530
Say something...

00:38:45.870 --> 00:38:47.320
Chi Yun!

00:39:04.120 --> 00:39:10.490
♪ Trapped in the loop of loneliness ♪

00:39:12.870 --> 00:39:18.720
♪ Trapped in the loop of loneliness ♪

00:39:18.720 --> 00:39:19.400
I'm sorry.

00:39:39.890 --> 00:39:40.750
Master Shao...

00:39:46.320 --> 00:39:48.180
Are you waiting for Shao Yanping?

00:39:48.920 --> 00:39:50.670
Too bad. He won't be coming.

00:39:51.760 --> 00:39:53.440
Yan used himself to test the medicine.

00:39:53.440 --> 00:39:55.100
His body is already very weak.

00:39:55.670 --> 00:39:57.330
We are no match for Xifang Tao.

00:39:58.030 --> 00:39:59.360
If Yan can escape,

00:39:59.880 --> 00:40:01.940
Tang Lici will be able to protect him.

00:40:13.510 --> 00:40:14.720
Yan, run!

00:40:16.770 --> 00:40:19.970
Sacrificing yourself just to
buy Liu Yan a chance to flee?

00:40:20.030 --> 00:40:21.190
I told you before,

00:40:21.440 --> 00:40:23.040
you should find another man.

00:40:23.630 --> 00:40:24.550
Silly girl,

00:40:25.320 --> 00:40:26.630
treating men like this

00:40:26.880 --> 00:40:28.880
only makes them care less about you.

00:40:29.150 --> 00:40:29.950
Be a smart girl

00:40:30.280 --> 00:40:31.670
in your next life.

00:40:34.720 --> 00:40:36.380
Heaven-Changing Scripture—

00:40:36.510 --> 00:40:39.280
Silver River Falls from the Ninth Heaven.

00:40:44.760 --> 00:40:45.440
Stop.

00:40:52.400 --> 00:40:53.110
Yan.

00:40:53.720 --> 00:40:54.650
Let Xiaohong go.

00:40:55.550 --> 00:40:56.400
It's been a long time,

00:40:56.400 --> 00:40:57.150
Master Liu.

00:41:03.760 --> 00:41:05.020
Who would have thought

00:41:05.070 --> 00:41:07.400
that the once noble and revered Master Liu

00:41:07.760 --> 00:41:09.490
would live in a place like this?

00:41:10.590 --> 00:41:12.120
This place is far too crude,

00:41:12.440 --> 00:41:14.400
hardly suitable for
developing the antidote.

00:41:14.400 --> 00:41:16.600
Come back to the Sword Alliance with me.

00:41:17.110 --> 00:41:19.170
Do you want to come with me on your own,

00:41:19.570 --> 00:41:21.100
or shall I take you by force?

00:41:25.150 --> 00:41:27.010
Do you choose to leave on your own,

00:41:27.630 --> 00:41:29.590
or do you choose to die here?

00:41:30.670 --> 00:41:31.920
Is this your last resort

00:41:31.920 --> 00:41:33.110
to save your life?

00:41:34.440 --> 00:41:35.280
At worst,

00:41:36.440 --> 00:41:38.110
we'll die together.

00:41:42.190 --> 00:41:43.390
I've changed my mind.

00:41:44.670 --> 00:41:45.660
Let Xiaohong go.

00:41:51.550 --> 00:41:52.230
Yan.

00:42:00.440 --> 00:42:01.030
Liu Yan.

00:42:03.470 --> 00:42:05.070
Did you become soft-hearted

00:42:05.880 --> 00:42:07.940
after experiencing great calamity,

00:42:07.990 --> 00:42:08.760
or have you

00:42:09.510 --> 00:42:11.070
always been this way?